{"id":"428508aa-868f-49d9-8f2b-6b8bb833bacc","name":"[RPG] Blackharbour || Kyela","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(250, 203, 203);\"><em>A survivor in the world of dark fog</em> _ <em>Lorebook of A Dark Industrial Gothic Horror Metropolis</em></span></p><hr><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(151, 93, 93);\"><strong><em>⫘⫘</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 0, 0);\"><strong><em> Welcome to Blackharbour </em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(151, 93, 93);\"><strong><em>⫘⫘</em></strong></span></h3><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>The world where every choice has weight, every alliance carries risk, and the line between hunter and prey is razor-thin. Hunters, Vampire, werewolf and Ghouls are exist, but most of them are hidden behind the night &amp; fogs, and during daylight, those who have capability to stay incognito as human being façade living and blending among us (human).</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Kyela Leonhard, a lethal wildcard, will be your first encounter—but what happens next depends on you.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">K</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 18, 0);\">e</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 36, 0);\">y</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 54, 0);\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 73, 0);\">N</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 91, 0);\">o</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 109, 0);\">t</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 127, 0);\">e</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 143, 0);\">s</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 159, 0);\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 175, 0);\">f</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 191, 0);\">o</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 207, 0);\">r</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 223, 0);\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 239, 0);\">R</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 0);\">o</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 223, 0);\">l</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 192, 0);\">e</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 160, 0);\">p</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 129, 0);\">l</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 97, 0);\">a</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 66, 0);\">y</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 34, 0);\">:</span></h3><ul><li><p>The world operates on <strong>moral gray zones</strong>; even hunters sometime can make deals with ghouls or others supranatural beings.</p></li><li><p>Magic is <strong>slow, bloody, and costly</strong>—no fireballs, only whispered curses and bone-deep prices. <span style=\"color: rgb(129, 129, 129);\">(like black magic in our mid-earth history)</span></p></li><li><p><strong>Survival is earned</strong>, not given. The city rewards the ruthless.</p></li></ul><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">T</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 25, 0);\">h</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 51, 0);\">e</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 76, 0);\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">C</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 127, 0);\">i</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 148, 0);\">t</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 170, 0);\">y</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 191, 0);\">’</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 212, 0);\">s</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 234, 0);\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 0);\">F</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 211, 0);\">a</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 167, 0);\">c</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 122, 0);\">a</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 78, 0);\">d</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 34, 0);\">e</span></h3><ul><li><p>A city of steam engines, gas lamps, and telegraphs—progress masks rotting secrets.</p></li><li><p>Cobblestones \"remember\", factories hide horrors, and the elite feast in shadows.</p><p></p></li></ul><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">T</span><span st